<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/3> legal:babHasTitle "HAK DAN KEWAJIBAN" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/3> legal:babHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/7> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/7> legal:pasalHasKey 7 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/7> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/7/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/7> .
