<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kekarantinaan Kesehatan di Pintu Masuk dan di wilayah dilakukan melalui kegiatan pengamatan penyakit dan Faktor Risiko Kesehatan Masyarakat terhadap Alat Angkut, orang, Barang, dan/atau lingkungan, serta respons terhadap Kedaruratan Kesehatan Masyarakat dalam bentuk tindakan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Tindakan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) berupa:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "Karantina, Isolasi, pemberian vaksinasi atau profilaksis, rujukan, disinfeksi, dan/atau dekontaminasi terhadap orang sesuai indikasi:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pembatasan Sosial Berskala Besar:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "disinfeksi, dekontaminasi, disinseksi, dan/atau deratisasi terhadap Alat Angkut dan Barang: dan/atau" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "penyehatan, pengamanan, dan pengendalian terhadap media lingkungan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/2/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Penyehatan, pengamanan, dan pengendalian terhadap media lingkungan sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (2) huruf d dilaksanakan sesuai dengan ketentuan peraturan perundang-undangan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan lebih lanjut mengenai tindakan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (2) diatur dengan Peraturan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
