<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/17/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/17/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kekarantinaan Kesehatan di Pintu Masuk diselenggarakan di Pelabuhan, Bandar Udara, dan Pos Lintas Batas Darat Negara." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/17/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/17/version/0/text> .
