<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Nakhoda menyampaikan permohonan untuk memperoleh Persetujuan Karantina Kesehatan atau memberitahukan suatu keadaan di Kapal dengan memakai isyarat sebagai berikut:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a> legal:pointHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "pada siang hari berupa:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/1> legal:pointHasKey "1" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Bendera O, yang berarti Kapal saya sehat atau saya minta Persetujuan Karantina Kesehatan," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/1> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/2> legal:pointHasKey "2" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Bendera O di atas panji pengganti kesatu, yang berarti Kapal saya tersangka, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/2> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/3> legal:pointHasKey "3" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Bendera O di atas Bendera L, yang berarti Kapal saya Terjangkit, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/3> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/a/point/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "pada malam hari berupa lampu merah di atas lampu putih dengan jarak maksimum 1,80 (satu koma delapan nol) meter, yang berarti saya belum mendapat Persetujuan Karantina Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/21/version/0/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22> legal:pasalHasKey 22 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Jika dalam waktu berlakunya Persetujuan Karantina Kesehatan timbul suatu kematian atau penyakit yang berpotensi menimbulkan Kedaruratan Kesehatan Masyarakat maka Persetujuan Karantina Kesehatan dapat dicabut dan dinyatakan tidak berlaku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kapal yang Persetujuan Karantina Kesehatannya dicabut dan dinyatakan tidak berlaku sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) wajib menuju ke suatu Zona Karantina untuk mendapat tindakan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/22/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23> legal:pasalHasKey 23 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kapal yang tidak mematuhi peraturan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan tidak diberikan Persetujuan Karantina Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kapal sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) diperintahkan supaya berangkat lagi atas tanggungan sendiri dan tidak diberikan izin memasuki Pelabuhan lain di wilayah Indonesia." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kapal sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) diberikan izin untuk mengambil bahan bakar, air, dan bahan makanan di bawah pengawasan Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/23/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/24> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/24> legal:pasalHasKey 24 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/24> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/24/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/24> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/24/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/24/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/24/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kekarantinaan Kesehatan terhadap kapal perang, kapal negara, dan kapal tamu negara diatur dengan Peraturan Menteri berkoordinasi dengan menteri atau lembaga terkait." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/24/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/24/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/1/paragraf> legal:paragrafSetHasParagraf <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/1/paragraf/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/1/paragraf/2> legal:paragrafHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/1/paragraf/2> legal:paragrafHasTitle "Paragraf 2 Keberangkatan Kapal" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/1/paragraf/2> legal:paragrafHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25> legal:pasalHasKey 25 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Sebelum keberangkatan Kapal, Nakhoda wajib melengkapi Dokumen Karantina Kesehatan yang masih berlaku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Setelah Dokumen Karantina Kesehatan sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) dinyatakan lengkap dan pada pemeriksaan oleh Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan tidak ditemukan indikasi Faktor Risiko Kesehatan Masyarakat maka kepada Nakhoda dapat diberikan Surat Persetujuan Berlayar Karantina Kesehatan (Port Health Ouarantine Clearance)." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam hal Kapal yang akan berangkat tidak dilengkapi dengan Surat Persetujuan Berlayar Karantina Kesehatan (Port Health OGuarantine Clearance) sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (2), syahbandar dilarang menerbitkan surat persetujuan berlayar." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/25/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
