<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26> legal:pasalHasKey 26 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0> .
