<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Apabila pada saat keberangkatan Kapal ditemukan adanya Faktor Risiko Kesehatan Masyarakat maka terhadap Kapal tersebut dilakukan tindakan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 15 ayat (2)." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Untuk Pelabuhan yang tidak memungkinkan dilakukan tindakan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan maka harus dilakukan di Pelabuhan tujuan berikutnya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/26/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian> legal:bagianSetHasBagian <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/2> legal:bagianHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/2> legal:bagianHasTitle "Bagian Kedua Pengawasan di Bandar Udara" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/2> legal:bagianHasParagrafSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/2/paragraf> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/2/paragraf> legal:paragrafSetHasParagraf <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/2/paragraf/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/2/paragraf/1> legal:paragrafHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/2/paragraf/1> legal:paragrafHasTitle "Paragraf 1 Kedatangan Pesawat Udara" .
