<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/27> legal:pasalHasKey 27 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/27> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/27/version/0> .
