<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap Pesawat Udara yang:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "datang dari Bandar Udara wilayah yang Terjangkit:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "terdapat orang hidup atau mati yang diduga Terjangkit: dan/atau" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "terdapat orang dan/atau Barang diduga Terpapar di dalam Pesawat Udara, berada dalam Status Karantina." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kapten Penerbang wajib segera melaporkan mengenai keadaan sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) kepada petugas lalu lintas udara untuk diteruskan kepada Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan di Bandar Udara tujuan dengan menggunakan teknologi telekomunikasi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/28/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29> legal:pasalHasKey 29 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Setelah kedatangan Pesawat Udara, Kapten Penerbang melalui pengelola Bandar Udara wajib memberikan dokumen Deklarasi Kesehatan Penerbangan (Health Part of the Aircraft General Declaration) kepada Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam hal kedatangan Pesawat Udara sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 28 ayat (1), Kapten Penerbang wajib secara langsung memberikan dokumen Deklarasi Kesehatan Penerbangan (Health Part of the Aircraft General Declaration) kepada Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/29/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30> legal:pasalHasKey 30 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kapten Penerbang pada Pesawat Udara sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 27 dan Pasal 28 hanya dapat menurunkan atau menaikkan orang dan/atau Barang setelah dilakukan Pengawasan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan oleh Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengawasan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) dilakukan untuk memperoleh Persetujuan Karantina Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Persetujuan Karantina Kesehatan sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (2) dapat berupa:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "persetujuan bebas karantina, dalam hal tidak ditemukan penyakit dan/atau faktor risiko yang berpotensi menimbulkan Kedaruratan Kesehatan Masyarakat dan/atau Dokumen Karantina Kesehatan dinyatakan lengkap dan berlaku, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "persetujuan karantina terbatas, dalam hal ditemukan penyakit dan/atau faktor risiko yang berpotensi menimbulkan Kedaruratan Kesehatan Masyarakat dan/atau Dokumen Karantina Kesehatan dinyatakan tidak lengkap dan tidak berlaku." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/3/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan lebih lanjut mengenai tata laksana Pengawasan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan di Bandar Udara diatur dengan Peraturan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/30/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/31> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/31> legal:pasalHasKey 31 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/31> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/31/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/31> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/31/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/31/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/31/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pesawat Udara yang memperoleh persetujuan karantina terbatas sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 30 ayat (3) huruf b harus dilakukan tindakan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan dan/atau penerbitan atau pembaruan Dokumen Karantina Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/31/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/31/version/0/text> .
