<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/32> legal:pasalHasKey 32 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/32> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/32/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/32> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/32/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/32/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/32/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kekarantinaan Kesehatan terhadap pesawat udara perang, pesawat udara negara, dan pesawat udara tamu negara diatur dengan Peraturan Menteri berkoordinasi dengan menteri atau lembaga terkait." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/32/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/32/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/2/paragraf> legal:paragrafSetHasParagraf <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/2/paragraf/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/2/paragraf/2> legal:paragrafHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/2/paragraf/2> legal:paragrafHasTitle "Paragraf 2 Keberangkatan Pesawat Udara" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/2/paragraf/2> legal:paragrafHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/33> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/33> legal:pasalHasKey 33 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/33> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/33/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/33> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/33/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/33/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/33/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Sebelum keberangkatan Pesawat Udara, Kapten Penerbang wajib melengkapi Dokumen Karantina Kesehatan sesuai standar Kekarantinaan Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/33/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/33/version/0/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/34> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/34> legal:pasalHasKey 34 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/34> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/34/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/34> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/34/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/34/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/34/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pesawat Udara yang ditemukan Faktor Risiko Kesehatan Masyarakat harus dilakukan tindakan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 15 ayat (2)." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/34/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/34/version/0/text> .
