<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap Kendaraan Darat yang:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "datang dari wilayah yang Terjangkit:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "terdapat orang hidup atau mati yang diduga Terjangkit, dan/atau" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString ". terdapat orang atau Barang diduga Terpapar di dalam Kendaraan Darat, berada dalam Status Karantina." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kendaraan Darat sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) harus dilakukan Pengawasan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan sebelum menurunkan atau menaikkan orang dan/atau Barang." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kendaraan Darat yang ditemukan Faktor Risiko Kesehatan Masyarakat pada Pengawasan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (2) harus dilakukan tindakan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap Kendaraan Darat di luar ketentuan sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) sewaktu-waktu dapat dilakukan pemeriksaan Faktor Risiko Kesehatan Masyarakat oleh Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/5> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasKey 5 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/5/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan lebih lanjut mengenai tindakan Kekarantinaan Kesehatan di Pos Lintas Batas Darat Negara sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) diatur dengan Peraturan Menteri." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/35/version/0/ayat/5/text> .
