<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Setelah kedatangan Kendaraan Darat, pengemudi wajib memberikan dokumen Deklarasi Kesehatan Perlintasan Darat (Ground Crossing Declaration of Health) kepada Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kendaraan Darat yang tidak ditemukan Faktor Risiko Kesehatan Masyarakat dan/atau dokumen Deklarasi Kesehatan Perlintasan Darat (Ground Crossing Declaration of Health) sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) dinyatakan lengkap diberikan Persetujuan Karantina Kesehatan oleh Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/36/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/3/paragraf> legal:paragrafSetHasParagraf <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/3/paragraf/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/3/paragraf/2> legal:paragrafHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/3/paragraf/2> legal:paragrafHasTitle "Paragraf 2 Keberangkatan Kendaraan Darat" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/6/bagian/3/paragraf/2> legal:paragrafHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> .
