<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/47> legal:pasalHasKey 47 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/47> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/47/version/0> .
