<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/48/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/48/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/48/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/48/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/48/version/0/ayat/2/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/48/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Setiap Kapten Penerbang yang melanggar ketentuan sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 28 ayat (2) atau Pasal 29 dikenai sanksi administratif berupa:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/48/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/48/version/0/ayat/2/point/description> .
