<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7> legal:babHasTitle "PENYELENGGARAAN KEKARANTINAAN KESEHATAN DI WILAYAH" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7> legal:babHasBagianSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7/bagian> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7/bagian> legal:bagianSetHasBagian <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7/bagian/1> .
