<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/49> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/49> legal:pasalHasKey 49 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/49> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/49/version/0> .
