<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/50> legal:pasalHasKey 50 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/50> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/50/version/0> .
