<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan wajib memberikan penjelasan kepada penghuni rumah sebelum melaksanakan tindakan Karantina Rumah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Penghuni rumah yang dikarantina selain kasus, dilarang keluar rumah selama waktu yang telah ditetapkan oleh Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/51/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52> legal:pasalHasKey 52 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Selama penyelenggaraan Karantina Rumah, kebutuhan hidup dasar bagi orang dan makanan hewan ternak yang berada dalam Karantina Rumah menjadi tanggung jawab Pemerintah Pusat." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Tanggung jawab Pemerintah Pusat dalam penyelenggaraan Karantina Rumah sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) dilakukan dengan melibatkan Pemerintah Daerah dan pihak yang terkait." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/52/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7/bagian> legal:bagianSetHasBagian <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7/bagian/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7/bagian/3> legal:bagianHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7/bagian/3> legal:bagianHasTitle "Bagian Ketiga Karantina Wilayah" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7/bagian/3> legal:bagianHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53> legal:pasalHasKey 53 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Karantina Wilayah merupakan bagian respons dari Kedaruratan Kesehatan Masyarakat." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Karantina Wilayah sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) dilaksanakan kepada seluruh anggota masyarakat di suatu wilayah apabila dari hasil konfirmasi laboratorium sudah terjadi penyebaran penyakit antar anggota masyarakat di wilayah tersebut." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/53/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54> legal:pasalHasKey 54 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan wajib memberikan penjelasan kepada masyarakat di wilayah setempat sebelum melaksanakan Karantina Wilayah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Wilayah yang dikarantina diberi garis karantina dan dijaga terus menerus oleh Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan dan Kepolisian Negara Republik Indonesia yang berada di luar wilayah karantina." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Anggota masyarakat yang dikarantina tidak boleh keluar masuk wilayah karantina." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Selama masa Karantina Wilayah ternyata salah satu atau beberapa anggota di wilayah tersebut ada yang menderita penyakit Kedaruratan Kesehatan Masyarakat yang sedang terjadi maka dilakukan tindakan Isolasi dan segera dirujuk ke rumah sakit." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/54/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55> legal:pasalHasKey 55 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Selama dalam Karantina Wilayah, kebutuhan hidup dasar orang dan makanan hewan ternak yang berada di wilayah karantina menjadi tanggung jawab Pemerintah Pusat." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Tanggung jawab Pemerintah Pusat dalam penyelenggaraan Karantina Wilayah sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) dilakukan dengan melibatkan Pemerintah Daerah dan pihak yang terkait." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/55/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7/bagian> legal:bagianSetHasBagian <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7/bagian/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7/bagian/4> legal:bagianHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7/bagian/4> legal:bagianHasTitle "Bagian Keempat Karantina Rumah Sakit" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/bab/7/bagian/4> legal:bagianHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56> legal:pasalHasKey 56 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Kegiatan Karantina Rumah Sakit merupakan bagian respons dari Kedaruratan Kesehatan Masyarakat." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Karantina Rumah Sakit sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) dilaksanakan kepada seluruh orang yang berkunjung, orang yang bertugas, pasien dan Barang, serta apapun di suatu rumah sakit bila dibuktikan berdasarkan hasil konfirmasi laboratorium telah terjadi penularan penyakit yang ada di ruang isolasi keluar ruang isolasi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/56/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57> legal:pasalHasKey 57 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan wajib memberikan penjelasan kepada orang yang berkunjung, orang yang bertugas di rumah sakit, dan pasien sebelum melaksanakan Karantina Rumah Sakit." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Rumah sakit yang dikarantina diberi garis karantina dan dijaga terus menerus oleh Pejabat Karantina Kesehatan, dan Kepolisian Negara Republik Indonesia yang berada di luar wilayah karantina." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Seluruh orang, Barang, dan/atau hewan yang berada di rumah sakit yang dikarantina sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (2) tidak boleh keluar dan masuk rumah sakit." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/57/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/58> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/58> legal:pasalHasKey 58 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/58> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/58/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/58> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/58/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/58/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/58/version/0/text> legal:textHasTextString "Selama dalam tindakan Karantina Rumah Sakit, kebutuhan hidup dasar seluruh orang yang berada di rumah sakit menjadi tanggung jawab Pemerintah Pusat dan/atau Pemerintah Daerah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/58/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/58/version/0/text> .
