<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "pelindungan kesehatan dari risiko kerusakan organ, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2018/6/pasal/76/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> .
